### 2. Avanan Email Threat Detected – Alert Only

**Category:** Email Security  
**RuleID:** 158025  
**Description:** Avanan detected an email threat (alert only)

```aql
SELECT "sourceIP" AS 'Source IP',
       LOGSOURCENAME(logsourceid) AS 'Log Source',
       QIDNAME(qid) AS 'Event Name',
       "Username",
       "Action",
       "Email Recipients",
       "Email Sender",
       "Event Type",
       "Product",
       "Subject",
       "Verdict",
       UTF8(payload) AS 'Payload',
       MIN(DATEFORMAT(devicetime,'yyyy-MMM-dd hh:mm a')) AS 'First Seen',
       MAX(DATEFORMAT(devicetime,'yyyy-MMM-dd hh:mm a')) AS 'Last Seen',
       COUNT(*) AS 'Event Count'
FROM events
WHERE INOFFENSE(#id#)
  AND logSourceId NOT IN (113, 63)
GROUP BY qid, logsourceid, "sourceIP", "Username", "Action",
         "Email Recipients", "Email Sender", "Event Type", "Product",
         "Subject", "Verdict", UTF8(payload)
ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
LIMIT 100
START '#start.time#' STOP '#last_persisted_time#';
```

